{"tid":2309345,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有「排汗困難、發熱身痕」嘅病友！","createTime":"2020-12-02T13:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T06:34:11.000Z","uid":89392,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9abe1cfda27404d346a1be07b0cb2a3545491a3","tid":2309345,"uid":89392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"冬天又嚟啦，你有冇排汗困難、發熱身痕嘅問題？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">迫地鐵、畀太陽曬、食辣、飲熱湯、做運動頭5分鐘、尷尬、緊張</span><br />\n<br />\n以上情況，係咪好似周身比針吉咁痕（尤其冬天）？但皮膚又冇疹冇癰？<br />\n<br />\n小弟患咗呢個病十幾年，睇過好多中醫。雖然未能根治，但總算有啲心得，希望幫到大家。<br />\n<br />\n不外乎四道板斧：<br />\n<br />\n1. 戒J。男人打J係呢個病嘅最大誘因。如果你係男，或多或少都知道打完第二日最痕。<br />\n2. 23:00前上床瞓覺。夜瞓係第二大誘因。<br />\n3. 忌食辛辣、<strong>羊肉</strong>、芒果、炸物（例如薯片、天婦羅）。<br />\n4. <span class=\"blue\"><strong>食淮山</strong></span>。唔好煮太耐，<span class=\"red\"><strong>留返少少黏液</strong></span>。我習慣切片烚1.5分鐘送公仔麵。食一至兩餐，會感覺出汗容易咗，冇咁痕。下圖呢種<strong>日本淮山</strong>尤其有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2483609/org/28476e390de2a97183966d28964b8faa.jpg/r1VJ0BPgyGUlem-VuFClAzZwKMCmwzgaUyYYF1MmGBc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2483609%2Forg%2F28476e390de2a97183966d28964b8faa.jpg%2Fr1VJ0BPgyGUlem-VuFClAzZwKMCmwzgaUyYYF1MmGBc&h=a3e1ce2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港街市最常見係中国淮山。呢隻日本貨又粗又淺色，價錢貴少少，但一條夠食三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n而家我一星期食一兩次淮山，加埋早訓、戒J、戒口，成功同呢個病保持距離。係有時定力唔夠，忍唔住破戒復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；不過堅持「四道板斧」一個禮拜就可以build up返。嚴格嚟講，算係治標唔治本，不過我已經好滿意了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人人身體唔同，我有效，唔保證你都有效。不過食一兩條淮山應該唔會死啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。呢個方法成本低，操作簡單，希望幫到大家。尤其是睇極醫生都冇起色嘅長期病友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：同日本淮山冇商業關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。試過有效、冇效，都不妨留言分享吓。"},{"pid":"3efc93d72676155cf71e37ac70bd41336f076d7b","tid":2309345,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"咁姐係咩原因"},{"pid":"9accea0172e8c4a2f14d5134edbb806912a9bce4","tid":2309345,"uid":89392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3efc93d72676155cf71e37ac70bd41336f076d7b","tid":2309345,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"咁姐係咩原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"我只係資深病人，唔係醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以好籠統咁形容為「陰虛內熱」。<br />\n四道板斧入面，打J、夜瞓係抽乾自己，食辣係點火。淮山係加返啲水。"},{"pid":"5ba58b15e755922ed7a53a524ef7f133d51ffd6f","tid":2309345,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"個人經驗係沖凍水涼，唔好沖熱水，不過比痕更辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d771fe285b67cc7b5af323dbb14d8afaf381fa","tid":2309345,"uid":58867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"唔覺有排汗困難<br />\n但有你講嘅發熱身痕症狀"},{"pid":"9eb873d5dcced5ceb465a38379597136a4d6ad66","tid":2309345,"uid":89392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T00:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c381b49f7e10140056b0032d57840313d2bde6b","tid":2309345,"uid":361000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T00:19:51.000Z","msg":"係蕁麻疹問題?"},{"pid":"4b464e580a1f8a85c3b87fab7d2f0be373c4bd27","tid":2309345,"uid":89392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1b85ce7ef6f0b7fcc00367f1fc1240cdfb2b2b","tid":2309345,"uid":133763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"有個方法簡單啲嘅<br />\n<br />\n就係做運動<br />\n<br />\n唔好比自己汗腺冬眠"},{"pid":"279816b2e0903bbc4c88f2865647b184abdd57fd","tid":2309345,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a1b85ce7ef6f0b7fcc00367f1fc1240cdfb2b2b","tid":2309345,"uid":133763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"有個方法簡單啲嘅<br />\n<br />\n就係做運動<br />\n<br />\n唔好比自己汗腺冬眠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:24:40.000Z","msg":"真，做運動最有用，習慣左 時間會越黎越短就出汗"},{"pid":"483a01acc79540a7c4c1630ab2042a989c6b6a93","tid":2309345,"uid":327527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"我有呢個問題啊 不過係冬天先會咁 所以一慨當係皮膚太乾引起既問題 <br />\n<br />\n所以答案只有一個 用 AQ 豬油膏 純潤冇藥性既野 喪搽搽搽搽"},{"pid":"ad8e19b961f91d30387451b82ec7db8a7801e42d","tid":2309345,"uid":134521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"冇打J但係會做愛 係咪應該搞少啲"}]}